{"tid":642830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"土地大辯論開波　牛鬼蛇神出籠","createTime":"2018-04-26T05:33:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-26T06:41:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"707bc298946e055ab278c15a126f4ad5b5cede30","tid":642830,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T05:33:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180426/20373395?_ga=2.108260098.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180426%2F20373395%3F_ga%3D2.108260098.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=pbNqoPxElrtkwPc8XrrD%2BNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=3a195aff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180426%2F20373395%3F_ga%3D2.108260098.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=b0c7b909\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180426/20373395?_ga=2.108260098.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n八方析時務：土地大辯論開波　牛鬼蛇神出籠<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180426/large/18618693.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180426%2Flarge%2F18618693.jpg&h=77bc599b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n粉嶺高爾夫球場<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n涉及龐大利益的土地供應，將於今天起展開一場大辯論。有政界預視未來五個月，政界會有不少「牛鬼蛇神」湧現，將對己方無着數的建議「扑低」，只餘己方可獨享利益的建議，目的是希望政府與他們談判，以開發己方最受惠的肥豬肉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n將無着數建議「扑低」<br />\n<br />\n有指這批「牛鬼蛇神」代表不同利益集團，背後人士毋須現身，隨時委託打手以環保、地區居民等人的利益，搖旗吶喊。就以開發貨櫃碼頭起樓選項為例，早前有富豪稱葵涌貨櫃碼頭上蓋可起樓，又有建築師說可將此打造為「天空之城」，之後又有與巨富關係密切的港鐵高層提出興建鐵路支線至貨櫃碼頭，不難令人懷疑已有人搶閘在背後發功。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又例如主流意見也支持開發的粉嶺高球場起樓建議，代表商界利益的權貴大力反對，據悉有商界議員與土地供應專責小組會面時，質疑小組擬在街站做問卷調查，等如變相公投，反稱填海才是最好、最快選擇，而周五就有香港高爾夫大聯盟亮相迎戰，各自搶攻輿論，將無着數建議逐個「扑低」。<br />\n<br />\n據知小組明日除公佈18項建議，還會建議要成立土地儲備，文件將不點名指曾蔭權年代如何停止開發土地，導致今日房屋困局，故將來要透過土地儲備，確保不造地的「曾蔭權2.0」不再出現。小組亦會委託港大就諮詢進行意見數據分析，同時與不同專業團體、社團會面，首月將以教育公眾為主軸。"},{"pid":"be4780d0bb495dab30d9e2a3a148c4a95baa5b53","tid":642830,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T06:18:05.000Z","msg":"泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/26/141804_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F141804_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=8e4cf102&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c6bd056d9a6feab292566968bbf2b01808c94680","tid":642830,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T06:21:43.000Z","msg":"大便論<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a56942d157af9868d39d313b30186e0d62b17665","tid":642830,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6bd056d9a6feab292566968bbf2b01808c94680","tid":642830,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T06:21:43.000Z","msg":"大便論<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T06:41:23.000Z","msg":"港共啲中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好介意咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}